# ============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================
# 
# Comments not appearing:
# - Check browser console for JavaScript errors
# - Verify repository has Discussions enabled
# - Ensure Giscus app is installed on your repository
# - Check GISCUS_REPO format: "username/repository-name"
# - Verify repository is public (required for Giscus)
# - Confirm discussion category exists
# 
# Environment validation errors:
# - Check console for detailed error messages
# - Verify environment variable names and values
# - Ensure boolean values use correct format ("true"/"false")
# - For Giscus booleans, use "1"/"0" format
# 
# Build or deployment issues:
# - Verify all required environment variables are set
# - Check that sensitive files are not committed
# - Ensure .gitignore includes all .env* files
# - Validate environment variable values in hosting platform
# 
# Performance issues:
# - Use GISCUS_LOADING=lazy for better performance
# - Consider disabling reactions if not needed
# - Monitor Core Web Vitals in browser dev tools
# 
# Need help?
# - Check the project documentation
# - Review browser console for error messages
# - Verify your configuration against working examples
# - Test with minimal configuration first